943
01:22:34,248 --> 01:22:36,889
Hello, I had to shovel all day yesterday.

944
01:22:36,949 --> 01:22:38,510
I need at least one day to play in this stuff.

945
01:22:39,230 --> 01:22:42,612
I mean, it's really funny what the kids will call up and say and do.

946
01:22:44,890 --> 01:22:45,190
You know?

947
01:22:45,230 --> 01:22:45,991
You understand?

948
01:22:46,011 --> 01:22:47,752
But that's what it is.

949
01:22:47,992 --> 01:22:48,333
Okay?

