1009
01:28:14,822 --> 01:28:22,807
So that's critical, you know, that we stress when we talk at the conference about adequacy being funding everyone because everyone can use the money.

1010
01:28:23,692 --> 01:28:28,676
You know, there's that John Greenleaf Whittier quote that I love so much, but I modify it.

1011
01:28:29,497 --> 01:28:33,821
John Greenleaf Whittier said, of all the sad words of tongue and pen, the saddest of these are what might have been.

1012
01:28:34,361 --> 01:28:35,002
I changed that.

1013
01:28:35,142 --> 01:28:39,445
