1014
01:28:40,246 --> 01:28:43,769
Because when they don't appropriate enough money, the language doesn't mean anything.

1015
01:28:44,610 --> 01:28:50,735
They've got to understand that communities like Medford may be wealthier than certain other communities,

1016
01:28:51,730 --> 01:28:54,211
Not as wealthy as others, but we need money.

1017
01:28:54,611 --> 01:29:06,913
