1022
01:29:26,484 --> 01:29:33,310
I mean, basically, we should be saying that all communities should receive an increase

1023
01:29:33,878 --> 01:29:38,281
that is consistent with the demands and the mandates that the state has put in place.

1024
01:29:38,561 --> 01:29:41,242
